Package de.feu.massim22.group3.utils.debugger

package de.feu.massim22.group3.utils.debugger
Provides classes of a debugging tool to visualize the agent environment, the current state of the simulation and also data of the decision process of the agents.
  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    de.feu.massim22.group3.utils
    Provides classes with helper methods and classes for debugging and logging.
    de.feu.massim22.group3.utils.debugger.debugData
    Provides data classes to communicate between the main program and the debugger.
    de.feu.massim22.group3.utils.logging
    Provides logging classes.
  • Class
    Description
    AgentPanel
    The Class AgentPanel defines a Panel to view debug information of an agent including its desires.
    AgentPanel.HeaderLabel
    The inner Class HeaderLabel defines a header text for labeling different sections of a panel
    CellUtils
    The Class CellUtils contains helper methods to draw cells of the massim simulation.
    DebugStepListener
    The Interface DebugStepListener defines methods for interaction between the GraphicalDebugger and a class which forwards information to the simulation server.
    GraphicalDebugger
    The Class GraphicalDebugger defines a Frame to view debug information of the current simulation and especially of Agents, their path finding and decision making.
    Header
    The Class Header defines a Panel which displays general information about the simulation, controls for manual interaction with the simulation and the selection of the displayed agent group.
    IGraphicalDebugger
    The Interface IGraphicalDebugger defines methods for communication between the debugger and the Navi.
    MapPanel
    The Class MapPanel defines a Panel which displays the simulation map.
    NormsPanel
    The Class NormsPanel defines a Panel which displays the current norms of the simulation.
    SimulationPanel
    The Class SimulationPanel defines a Panel which displays information about the current simulation including norms and tasks.
    TaskPanel
    The Class TaskPanel defines a Panel which displays information about the current tasks of the simulation.
